<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome | Task Manager</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #333, #1a1a1a);
            color: cyan;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #457b9d, #1d3557);
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .cta-buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            color: cyan;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .cta-buttons a.btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, blue, cyan);
        }
        .cta-buttons a.btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, cyan, blue);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .cta-buttons a.btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #06d6a0, #118ab2);
        }
        .cta-buttons a.btn-secondary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #118ab2, #06d6a0);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .feature-box h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feature-box p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #d1d1d1;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #1d3557;
            color: #d1d1d1;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #06d6a0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { user: user }) %> <!-- Correct path -->

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Task Manager</h1>
        <p>Task Manager is your ultimate productivity tool designed to help you organize, prioritize, and conquer your daily tasks with ease.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-primary">Logout</a>
                <span style="color: cyan; font-size: 1.2rem;">Welcome, <%= user.name %></span>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-secondary">Register</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Effortless Task Tracking</h3>
            <p>Manage your tasks seamlessly with a user-friendly interface that keeps everything organized.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Stay Ahead of Deadlines</h3>
            <p>Set due dates and reminders to ensure you never miss an important task again.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Collaborative Features</h3>
            <p>Share tasks with team members and stay updated on progress in real time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Secure and Reliable</h3>
            <p>We prioritize your data security with cutting-edge encryption and backup systems.</p>
        </div>
    </section>


    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Task Manager. All rights reserved. | <a href="/about">About Us</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
